import pandas as pd
import os
files = os.listdir('resubmit_data')
dfs = []
for i in files:
    dfs.append(pd.read_pickle(f'resubmit_data/{i}'))

winners =[]
winning_dfs = []
for ind, df in enumerate(dfs):
    if (df.min() == df.iloc[0, :]).all():
        winners.append(ind)
        winning_dfs.append(df)

windict = {}
for i,j in zip([files[i] for i in winners],winning_dfs):
    windict[i] = j

counter = 0
for data,forecasts in (zip(winning_paths, winning_forc_paths)):
    display(HTML(f"<h2>{data}</h2>"))
    display(winning_dfs[counter])
    counter+=1
    dta = pd.read_csv(f'C:\\Users\\zaneh\\OneDrive\\Documents\\York_PhD\\Spring_2023\\Metaculus\\questions\\{data}')
    dta['Time'] = pd.to_datetime(dta.Time)
    dta = dta[dta.grouping == 'forecasters']
    dta['uniform_step'] = np.arange(0,len(dta.Time),1)
    res = int(dta['resolution'].iloc[0]) 
    intres = res
    res = '\nResolved Yes' if res == 1 else '\nResolved No'
    fig,ax = plt.subplots(1,1, figsize = (15,5))
    ax.scatter(dta.uniform_step, dta.Prediction, c= 'black', s = 100)
    ax.set_title(str.replace(str.split(data,'_.csv')[0], '_', ' ') + res, fontsize = 15)

    # the forecasts 

    fs = pd.read_pickle(f'forecast_data/{forecasts}').T
    fs.columns = ['indx', 'kairosmedian', 'kairosmean', 'uwmedian', 'uwmean', 'twentymedian', 'twentymean', 'geommedian', 'geommean']
    fs = fs.set_index('indx')
    fs = fs[['kairosmedian','twentymedian','uwmedian','geommedian']]
    ax.plot(fs, label = fs.columns, lw = 4)
    ax.legend(ncol = 8)
    plt.show()
